verbose_text: These include an increase in proliferation of resident tissue fibroblasts, a reduced level of metalloproteinases synthesis (MMP-1 and MMP-2), resulting in low levels of extracellular matrix degrading, an increase in collagen type I production, heat-shock protein 47 (hsp47) production, and other extracellular matrix components [XREF_BIBR].
